    <h1>About D Cam Engineering</h1>
    <p style="max-width:780px">D Cam Engineering is a sole-proprietorship firm founded in <%= company.established %> in Ahmedabad, Gujarat, led by <%= company.proprietor %>. We are an in-house manufacturer, supplier and exporter of high-pressure and laboratory equipment — core holders, floating piston accumulators, high pressure syringe pumps, core flooding apparatus, permeameters and stirred reactors — used in oil &amp; gas research, petroleum / EOR studies and geotechnical laboratories.</p>

